criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  adults with a first/recurrent TIA or minor stroke;

          -  identified within 6 months of their diagnosis;

          -  who consent to take part

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  diagnosis of dementia;

          -  receiving psychological interventions for mental health difficulties immediately prior
             to their TIA/minor stroke, visual or hearing impairments that would impact on ability
             to complete baseline assessments;

          -  cognitive or communication difficulties that would impact on ability to complete
             baseline assessments and to participate in group sessions;

          -  unable to communicate in English.
